name: StuRa-Baracke (Haus der Jugend)

name: Images Cinema
directions: Go past two sets of front doors and the inner lobby door, it will be the second door on your left (not the Red Herring door).
comment:
The single stall bathroom is free for anyone to use! Just ask the box office staff member on duty if it’s okay first if you’re not seeing a movie.

The theater is typically only open from around 1pm to 11pm (check out imagescinema.org for more accurate times), but the MASS MoCA By Design staff member next door should be able to let you use the bathroom if nobody is at Images yet.
